          "COMMENT": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "-By Authors- As a Check of the Beam Monitoring Method,",
                "The Cross Section of the Reaction 12-Mg-0(P,X)11-Na-22",
                "Was Measured Near 20 MeV. It was Found by 20% Higher",
                "Than the Result of Batzel+, See Rel-Ref. To Take this",
                "Discrepancy Into Account, the Measured Fission Cross",
                "Sections were Reduced by 10%.",
                "-By Compiler- The Discrepancy Mentioned by Authors",
                "Originates Most Likely from the Defect in the",
                "Monitoring Data, Mentioned by Hille+ - See Rel-Ref -",
                "The Monitor Reaction Data of Ghoshal+ are Shifted",
                "Systematically Towards Higher Energies by 1-1.5  MeV,",
                "Probably Due to the Old Stopping-Power Values Used to",
                "Calculate the Energy Loss in the Foils."
              ]
            }
          ],
